Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=20}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.51,0:01:54.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– He won!\N– He won!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:59.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Arlong Park has fallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.06,0:02:02.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We did it, older sister! - OG}We did it, Nojiko!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:02.60,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{Gen-san! - OG}Mr. Gen!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.98,0:02:06.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This... This isn't a dream, is it?{OG}{This... This isn't a dream, right? - Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.69,0:02:08.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I never thought this\Nday would come...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.79,0:02:25.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Way to go, Luffy!\NYou get my praise, too! - OG}{Way to go, Luffy! I'll throw\Nin my compliments, too! - Gaijin}Way to go, Luffy!\NYou backed me up perfectly!{Goldy}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:31.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{[/q2] - Though I'd be praising you even more if you would've been the star performer instead of me!  - OG}{Though, I'd praise you even more if you\Nwould've given me more of a starring role! - Gaijin}{\q2}Although, as the star of the show, I could've\Nused a little more time in the spotlight!{nao+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.76,0:02:34.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Man, talk about being\Non pins and needles... - OG}Man, talk about a nail-biter...{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.93,0:02:39.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Take care of things quicker\Nfrom now on, you damn jerk! - OG}Next time, wrap it up a bit\Nquicker, you damn jerk!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:10.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:25.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hold it right there, you! - OG}{Hold it right there, you lot! - Dan: Fits better 貴様ら in the phrase}Alright, that's enough of that!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:27.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He's...! - OG}{It's that guy...! - Gaijin}It's him...!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:30.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What a lucky day today is! - OG}Today's my lucky day!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:34.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Well done. I watched the entire fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:39.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Fluke as it was, I never once\Nimagined the fishmen would lose - OG}Fluke or not, I never once\Nimagined the fishmen would lose{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:42.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{to a bunch of nameless\Npirates like you. - OG}to a band of no-name pirates like you.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.04,0:03:46.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{However, thanks to you,\Nall the money I was to give Arlong - OG}However, thanks to you, I don't have\Nto give any money to Arlong,{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:50.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{and all the money and valuables\Nstored in Arlong Park is now mine! - OG}{and anything of value found\Nin Arlong Park is now mine! - Gaijin}and all the valuables in\NArlong Park are now mine!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:52.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Everyone drop your weapons! - OG}Drop your weapons!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:55.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I, Captain Nezumi\Nof Marine Branch #16, - OG}The credit for this incident\Nnow belongs to me,{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.51,0:03:57.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{hereby take credit for\Nwhat you've done here! - OG}{Captain Nezumi of the\NMarines' 16th Branch! - Gaijin}Captain Nezumi of the Marines' 16th–{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:00.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:04.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't ruin people's fun\Nwhen they're finally happy! - OG}{Dan: Maybe "rejoicing" instead of "happy" would be better}{Don't rain on people's parade\Nwhile they're rejoicing! - Gaijin}We're celebrating our victory.\NDon't ruin our fun.{Viz+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:15.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{J-just you try laying a\Nfinger on me! You'll be sorry! - OG}{J-Just you try to lay a finger\Non me! You'll be sorry! - Gaijin}Y-You just try and lay a finger\Non me! You'll regret it!{nao+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:16.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He's still sayin' it? - OG}{Are you still talking? - Gaijin}Still running your mouth?{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:22.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This is for shooting Nojiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:27.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{and tearing up Bell-mère-san's\Ntangerine orchard. - OG}and for tearing up Bell-mère's\Ntangerine grove.{Gaijin+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:28.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.96,0:04:32.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:39.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Nami! That felt good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:42.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Give 'im 1,000 more of those! - OG}Give him another thousand of those!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:51.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You guys are gonna clean\Nup after those fishmen now! - OG}You Marines are gonna clean\Nup after these fishmen now!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:54.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And you're gonna help\Nrebuild the town of Gosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:58.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{And you're not gonna touch any\Nmoney or valuables in Arlong Park! - OG}{And you're not gonna touch\Nanything of value in Arlong Park! - Gaijin}And don't even think about touching\Nany valuables in Arlong Park!{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:05:00.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's the island's money! Got it?! - OG}That money belongs to\Nthe island! You hear me?!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:04.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Ow! Ow! I-I'll do what you say! - OG}Ow! Ow! L-Loud and clear!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:05.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{And one other thing! - OG}And one last thing!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:08.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Give me my money back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:13.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'll give it back! I'll give it back!\NI don't care anymore... - OG}I'll give it back! I'll give it back!\NIt's not worth it anymore...{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:19.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'll get you, you rotten pirates! - OG}You're gonna pay, you rotten pirates!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.51,0:05:22.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Straw hat man!\NYour name's Luffy, right?! - OG}You, with the straw hat!\NYour name's Luffy, right?!{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.47,0:05:25.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're the captain, right?!\NDon't forget this! - OG}{You're the captain,\Nright?! Remember this! - Gaijin}I take it you're the captain?!\NMark my words!{Polly+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.10,0:05:28.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Some major stuff's gonna happen\Nto you now! You've made me mad! - OG}{You're in for quite the ride!\NYou've pushed me too far! - Gaijin}Big things are in store for you!\NYou've made me mad!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:30.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{It's too late to regret\Nwhat you've done! - OG}It's too late for regrets!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:34.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{I'm gonna get revenge on you!\NJust you wait and see! - OG}I will have my revenge!\NJust you wait and see!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.19,0:05:36.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Says some major\Nstuff's gonna happen now. - OG}{He says we're in for quite the ride. - Gaijin}Big things are in store, he says.{nao+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:40.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,How does he know I'm gonna\Nbe King of the Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:42.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's not what he means!\NMan, you're stupid! - OG}That's not what he means, dumbass!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:46.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{H-Hey, what do we do?! What if we\Nreally do wind up in big trouble?! - OG}H-Hey, what do we do?! What if\Nsomething really does happen?!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:48.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Hey! Hey, I said! - OG}{Hey! Hey! What'll we do?! - Gaijin}Huh?! Huh?! Tell me!{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:53.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Alright, everyone! This is no time\Nfor us to be the only ecstatic ones! - OG}{Dan: Maybe "Wouldn't it be bad for us to be the only ones celebrating?"}{Alright, everyone!\NWe can't have all the fun! - Gaijin}Alright, everyone!\NWe can't go having all the fun!{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:56.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We need to tell everyone on the\Nisland about this big incident! - OG}{Everyone on the island needs to\Nknow about this monumental event! - Gaijin}Let's tell the whole island\Nwhat happened here!{Z+Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:00.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Arlong Park...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:02.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Arlong Park has fallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:08.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Taken from dub}{Hey Zoro, what's that on your chest? - OG}You hurting anywhere, Zoro? Here?{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:08.06,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{Taken from dub}{Huh? Hey, what are you-? - OG}Huh? What're you– Hey!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.19,0:06:19.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Good for you, Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:24.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{To think we'd end up\Nbeing saved by pirates... - OG}I can't believe we were\Nsaved by pirates...{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:26.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You never know\Nwhat's gonna happen next. - OG}{Dan:It's good as is, but may need rephrasing to be a bit shorter}Life's full of surprises.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:46.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What?! You're still here, Nami? - OG}Really, Nami? You're still here?{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:49.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Your friends've been\Nlooking for you, you know. - OG}Your friends have been\Nlooking for you.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:53.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Say, Nojiko... - OG}Hey, Nojiko...{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:53.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:54.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Gen-san... - OG}Mr. Gen...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:06:55.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:57.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If Bell-mère-san were alive, - OG}If Bell-mère was still with us,{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:07:00.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{do you think she would stop\Nme from being a pirate? - OG}do you think she'd stop\Nme from being a pirate?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:02.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A pirate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.24,0:07:04.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:08.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Of course she'd never let her\Nprecious daughter be a pirate! - OG}There's no way she'd ever let her\Nprecious daughter be a pirate!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:09.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,She wouldn't stop you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:09.91,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,Nojiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.91,0:07:11.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Even if she did... - OG}Even if she tried...{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:13.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,would you really listen to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:17.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Absolutely not! - OG}Hell no!{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:21.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What's with you, Gen-san? - OG}What's so funny, Mr. Gen?{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:31.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You two are definitely\NBell-mère's kids, all right. - OG}You two are definitely\NBell-mère's kids, alright.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:33.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Gen-san? - OG}Mr. Gen?{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.27,0:07:34.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.23,0:07:36.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You've already made\Nup your mind right? - OG}You've already made up\Nyour mind, haven't you?{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:38.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Then live how you want. - OG}Then live how you want to.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:40.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Just as your mother did! - OG}Just like your mother.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:48.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He's still at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:52.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Sounds like ol' Zoro's really hurtin'. - Dan: Not sure if it's fine to phrase it like that, maybe just "Sounds like Zoro's in a lot of pain". Gaijin: It's fine for me.}Sounds like Zoro's going through it.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:53.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Well, yeah. - OG}You said it.{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:56.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{A normal person with those wounds\Nwould take two years to fully heal! - OG}{An average person with those wounds\Nwould take two years to fully heal! - Gaijin}It'd normally take two years to heal from those wounds!{PP+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:07:59.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You fool! - OG}You moron!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:02.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Trying to take care of such\Na big injury on your own...! - OG}{Trying to take care of such\Na grave injury on your own! - Gaijin}Trying to treat such\Na grave injury on your own...{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:04.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.09,0:08:07.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Honestly! Are you folks\Nreally pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:08.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Don't you even have...{OG}{Do you even have... - Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:10.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{a ship doctor?! - OG}{a ship's doctor?! - Gaijin}a doctor on board?!{Goldy+Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:12.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{A doctor? That sounds good, too! - OG}A doctor? That'd be nice, too!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:13.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:16.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,But a musician comes\Nfirst. Right, Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:17.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Why's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:19.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Pirates sing, you know? - OG}{Because pirates sing, you know! - Dan: Maybe adding a "Because" to the beginning of the sentence}'Cause pirates sing! Duh!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:22.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So why does that come first?! - OG}Okay, but why does that come first?!{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:24.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hello?! Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.32,0:08:26.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes. This is Marine Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:27.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Headquarters?! Marine Headquarters?! - OG}HQ?! Is this Marine HQ?!{nao - Should be okay, they say the full name in the previous line}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.95,0:08:32.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hello! This is Captain Nezumi\Nof Marine Branch #16! - OG}Hello! This is Captain\NNezumi of the 16th Branch!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:35.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Marine code 00733!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.62,0:08:36.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I have a request for HQ!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:39.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{[/q2]You don't need to shout. I can hear you. - OG}{\q2\i1}No need to shout. I can hear you.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:43.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{[/pos(720,1071.3)]Listen! There's a pirate named\NLuffy, who wears a straw hat! - OG}{\pos(720,1071.3)}Listen! There's a pirate wearing\Na straw hat named Luffy!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:47.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{[/pos(720,1071.3)]Listen! There's a pirate named\NLuffy, who wears a straw hat! - OG}{\pos(720,1071.3)\i1}Listen! There's a pirate wearing\Na straw hat named Luffy!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.47,0:08:51.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I deem him and his four crew members\Nas enemies of the government! - OG}I deem him and his four crew\Nmembers enemies of the government!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:57.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{[/i1/pos(720,1071.3)] - I deem him and his four crew members\Nas enemies of the government! - OG}{\i1\pos(720,1071.3)}I deem him and his four crew\Nmembers enemies of the government!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.06,0:08:58.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,"Luffy..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.56,0:09:03.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{They managed to take down Arlong, the fishman of Arlong Park who was purported to be invincible! - OG}{They managed to take down the purportedly invincible Arlong Pirates, the fishmen of Arlong Park! - Gaijin}They took down Arlong Park's supposedly\Ninvincible fishmen, the Arlong Pirates!{nao+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:06.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Based on their\Nthreat and dangerousness, - OG}{Considering this threat, I have placed - Gaijin}Given the threat that they pose,{nao+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:10.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{a large bounty has been placed on\Ntheir captain, Straw Hat Luffy! - OG}{a hefty bounty on the\Ncaptain, Straw Hat Luffy! - Gaijin}I've placed a sizable bounty\Non the captain, Straw Hat Luffy!{nao+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:11.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Now sending a photograph! - OG}{I'm now sending a photograph! - Gaijin}Sending a photograph now!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:12.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:17.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:20.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Couldn't you have taken a better one than that?! - OG}{Couldn't you have taken a better one?! - Gaijin}You couldn't get\Na better shot than that?!{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:22.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No, that's all I could get... - OG}No, sir. I'm afraid not...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:26.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After a quick verification,\NI will submit it for approval.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:31.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't forget, now! He's a\Nvile pirate! "Dead or Alive"! - OG}Don't forget! He's a rotten pirate,\Nso it's dead or alive!{Z+nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:37.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Put him on wanted\Nposters throughout the world! - OG\i1}Put him on wanted posters\Nacross the globe!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:51.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Whew, I'm stuffed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:55.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Sometimes it's nice to only eat! - OG}{Sometimes it's nice to just eat! - Gaijin}It's nice to just eat for a change.{Goldy}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:56.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Are your wounds all better now, Zoro? - OG}Are your wounds healed up, Zoro?{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:59.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This's nothin'! Some food\Nand drink'll fix it right up! - OG}Some food and drink'll fix me right up.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:01.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah? - OG}That so?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:04.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But how long is this\Ndumb party gonna last? - OG}But seriously, how long\Nis this stupid party gonna last?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:06.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This is the third day now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:08.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.05,0:10:11.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{When you wanna celebrate,\Nyou should go all out. - OG}{When you wanna celebrate, you\Nshould pull out all the stops. - Gaijin}If you're gonna celebrate,\Nmight as well pull out all the stops.{nao+Goldy}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:15.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sanji! That melon you just had!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:16.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Was there something on it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.89,0:10:19.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What's with the meat in your hands?! - OG}What's with all that meat?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.27,0:10:22.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Sure was. It's "raw ham melon,"\Nso there was raw ham on it. - OG}{Sure was. It's prosciutto and melon,\Nso there was prosciutto on it. - Gaijin}Sure was. It's prosciutto and melon,\Nso there was dry-cured ham on it.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:25.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Raw ham melon?! That sounds yum!\NWh-Where did you get it?! - OG}{Prosciutto and melon?! That sounds\Ngreat! Wh-Where did you get it?! - Gaijin}Ham and melon?! Sounds yummy!\NWh-Where's it at?!{nao+Goldy}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:26.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Dunno... - OG}I dunno.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:31.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The whole village is a buffet\Nparty, so I dunno where I got it... - OG}{\q2}The village is one big buffet party right now.\NCouldn't tell you where I got it.{nao+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:33.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He's long gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:36.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He's been eating non-stop\Nfor three days straight! - OG}He's been eating non-stop\Nfor three days!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:39.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Now, then. I'm done eating. - OG}As for me, that's enough food.{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:40.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Now I think I'll... - OG}It's about time I...{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:42.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{pick up some girls! - OG}go charm the ladies!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.58,0:10:46.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I am Captain Usopp, hero of love and courage - OG}{I am Captain Usopp,\Nthe lovable and courageous hero - Gaijin}It is I, Captain Usopp!\NThe lovable and courageous hero{nao+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:50.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{who finished off\Nthe strongest fishman boss! - OG}{who brought down the\Nstrongest fishman officer of all! - Gaijin}who defeated the strongest\Nfishman leader of all!{nao+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:46.58,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Way to go, kiddo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:48.34,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Can I have your autograph?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:54.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Here's an Usopp Support Song! - OG}{Here's an Usopp anthem! - Gaijin}Now how about an Usopp anthem?!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.93,0:11:00.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(150,150)\b1\bord3.375\shad2.7\fnFOT-Greco Std B Strp\fs74.25}♪ Who was it? Who was it? ♪\N♪ Who beat the fishman? ♪
Comment: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:07.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[More of Usopp's song, untranslated.]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.14,0:11:00.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hmph. How boring. - OG}What a bore.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:01.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:04.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd be more\Ndown in the dumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.23,0:11:08.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Like, "Why didn't this happen\Nbefore my dad died?!" - OG}Like, "Why couldn't this have\Nhappened before my daddy died?!"{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:09.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:13.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That's how I felt at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:15.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,But now I'm thinking about the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.99,0:11:17.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,The future?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:21.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We've been saved by that\Nstraw hat guy and his friends. - OG}That straw hat guy\Nand his friends helped us out.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:26.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But starting tomorrow, we have\Nto start from scratch on our own. - OG}But tomorrow, we need\Nto make a fresh start by ourselves.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:31.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{There's no way we can forget\Nwhat's happened in the past, and I don't think we need to. - OG}There's no way we can forget the\Npast, and I don't think we need to.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:35.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But, I think what's most important\Nis what happens from now on! - OG}{But what's important\Nis what comes next! - Gaijin}What matters most\Nis what comes next!{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.51,0:11:38.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What we do now.\NWhat things we need to do. - OG}{What should we do?\NWhat do we need to do? - Gaijin}What now? What do we need to do?{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:42.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{[/i1]We're[/i0] the ones who're gonna\Nsupport the villages now, - OG}{[/i1]We're[/i0] the ones who're gonna\Nsustain our villages now. - Gaijin}From now on, {\i1}we're{\i0} the ones\Nwho'll keep our villages going.{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:44.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{so I decided to\Nthink that way instead! - OG}{That's the approach I'm gonna take. - Gaijin}That's how I see it, at least.{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:47.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Cheeky kid! - OG}{You're so precocious! - Gaijin}Smartass!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:48.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Oww! - OG}Ow! Ow! Ow!{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:51.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Why're you pinching me?!\NI don't understand! Why?! - OG}Why are you pinching me?!\NI don't understand! Why?!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:54.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{And here I was hoping to harass\Nyou some more for good measure! - OG}{And here I was just\Nhoping to tease you again! - Gaijin}And here I was hoping\Nto tease you again!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.11,0:11:58.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You've harassed me plenty,\Nyou dumb tattoo punk girl! - OG}{You've teased me plenty,\Nyou dumb, tattooed punk girl! - Gaijin}You've teased me plenty,\Nyou inked-up punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.04,0:12:05.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{"Punk" will do just fine! - OG}{I'm okay with "punk"! - Gaijin}"Punk" is fine by me!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:09.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Will it come off?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:13.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'd like to say, "No problem," - OG}I wish I could say it'd be no problem,{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:15.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{but there's no way\Nto remove it fully. - OG}{but there's no way to\Nremove it altogether. - Gaijin}but I can't fully remove it.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:16.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.97,0:12:20.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I know it's stupid of me.\NThey stay on for life. - OG}{I know it's stupid of me.\NThey're there for life. - Gaijin}I know it's stupid of me.\NIt'll be with me for life.{Goldy}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.97,0:12:23.76,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,I don't want anyone to see this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:27.56,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,This... This tattoo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:31.77,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm not even\Nreally Arlong's friend... - OG}I don't even want\Nto be in Arlong's crew,{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:34.23,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,but it's like I've been branded a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:37.24,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:42.20,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Nojiko! What is that?! - OG}Nojiko! What's that?!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:43.08,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Oh? You mean this? - OG}What, this?{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:47.04,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's no big deal! It's just a decoration! - OG}It's no big deal!\NIt's just a bit of art!{Z+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:48.96,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Now me and you are the same! - OG}{Now I'm just like you! - Gaijin}Now we're matching!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:57.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Say, Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:13:00.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{There's a tattoo I'd like to have. - OG}There {\i1}is{\i0} a tattoo that I want.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:02.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.89,0:13:05.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Those two can dance! - OG}Those two sure can dance!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:09.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Here's Usopp Support Song #185! - OG}{Here's Usopp Anthem No. 185! - Gaijin}Time for Usopp Anthem No. 185!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:15.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bell-mère...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:20.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Your daughters have grown up\Nto be truly strong and respectable! - OG}{Your girls have grown up to be\Npositively tough and honorable. - Gaijin}Your little girls have grown\Ninto tough, honorable women.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.41,0:13:24.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's almost as if\NI'm seeing you in life again! - OG}{They remind me of you. - Gaijin}It's like you're still here with us.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:28.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We're going to live life to\Nits fullest from now on. - OG}From here on out, we're gonna\Nlive life to the fullest.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.29,0:13:32.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We've lost and sacrificed\Nfar too much. - OG}We're only here because of\Nhow much we've sacrificed.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:38.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Which is why we're going to smile\Nas insanely much as possible now. - OG}{Which is why we're gonna smile\Nand laugh like the idiots we are! - Gaijin}And that's exactly why we're\Ngonna smile and laugh like idiots!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:41.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Raw ham melon! - OG}{Prosciutto and melon! - Gaijin}Ham and melon!{Goldy}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.93,0:13:46.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Huh? There's no food around here.\NThat's no good. Time to go back. - OG}Wha...? There's no food around here.\NAw, crap. Guess I'll head back...{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:47.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hold it, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:51.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{A grave? Did someone die? - OG}A grave? Did somebody die?{Goldy}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:54.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah. A long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.69,0:13:59.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh, my deepest conveniences.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.53,0:14:04.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Huh? Deepest concussions.\NHuh? Deepest compli– - OG}Uh... Deepest compliments.\NWait. Deepest concussio–{Goldy+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.16,0:14:06.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Deepest condolences.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.41,0:14:08.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That. - OG}{That's what I meant. - Gaijin}Yeah, that.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.12,0:14:09.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:13.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Nami is going to ride your ship.\NShe's going to be a pirate. - OG}Nami is going aboard your ship.\NShe's going to be a pirate.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:15.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It'll be a dangerous journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:18.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's fine. - OG}There's no way around that.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:20.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{There's no way around that. - OG}I get it. But know this.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.76,0:14:24.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But, if you guys ever do anything\Nto take away Nami's smile... - OG}If you guys ever do anything\Nto take away her smile,{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:26.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I [/i1]will[/i0] come kill you! - OG}{I [/i1]will[/i0] kill you! - Gaijin}I'll kill you myself!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:29.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. I'm not gonna take it away, though. - OG}{Yeah. I'm not gonna do that, though. - Gaijin}Sure. I'm not gonna do that, though.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:31.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:34.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:11.31,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Wow! Today's a big feast! - OG}Wow! So much food today!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:14.56,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Do you two know what today is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:18.69,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Today is the day I first met you two! - OG}It's the anniversary\Nof the day I met you!{Z+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:21.69,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's the day you two\Nbecame my daughters! - OG}The day you two\Nbecame my daughters!{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:22.57,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:28.41,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,C'mon, stop crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.41,0:15:31.54,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{A storm destroyed\Nthe orchard. So what? - OG}A storm destroyed\Nthe grove. So what?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.54,0:15:36.00,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{You need to be strong girls who\Ncan smile even through hard times! - OG}I need you girls to be strong\Nand smile even when times are tough!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:40.25,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Do that, and the nice\Nthings will come to you! - OG}Do that, and I'm sure\Nyou'll find happiness!{nao - Resembling AP05 @08:40}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:43.92,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{It'll come, I promise! - OG}You will. I promise!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:46.76,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Nami! Could you get me the salt? - OG}Nami! Mind getting me the salt?{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:50.72,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{First you learned how to draw\Nsea charts, and now land maps! - OG}First you learned to draw\Nsea charts, and now land maps!{Polly}{AP04 @06:33}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:54.27,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm studying navigation too now! - OG}I've been studying navigation, too!{Gaijin}{AP04 @06:47}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:56.39,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Navigation, too?! - OG}Even navigation?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:58.35,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{It is Nami's dream! - OG}That's Nami's dream, after all!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:02.94,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna use my navigational skills\Nto travel to all the world's oceans! - OG}I'm gonna use my navigation skills\Nto sail all the world's seas!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:06.57,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{And then I'm gonna make a\Nworld map of everything I see! - OG}And then I'll make a map\Nof everything I see!{Polly+Goldy}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:11.53,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{So your map of this island is your\Nfirst step toward your dream, then? - OG}That means this map of the island\Nis the first step toward your dream!{Polly+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:13.04,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.07,0:16:46.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's all over, Bell-mère-san. - OG}It's over, Bell-mère.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.32,0:16:50.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It took eight years,\Nbut we're finally free!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:53.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Me, and all the others... - OG}Me, and everyone else...{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:55.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's exactly like you said. - OG}It's just like you said.{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:59.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{"If you live through it,\Nnice things will come." - OG}"If we survive, we'll be\Nhappy someday."{nao - Referencing AP05 @08:36}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:01.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You were right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.21,0:17:04.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{All the villagers are smiling so happily\Nfrom the bottom of their hearts! - OG}All the villagers are smiling from\Nthe bottom of their hearts!{nao}
Comment: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:08.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{And me! - OG}As for me,{nao}
Comment: 0,0:17:08.55,0:17:10.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm thinking of leaving this island! - OG}I think I might leave the island!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:10.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{And me! I'm thinking\Nof leaving this island! - OG}As for me, I'm thinking\Nof leaving the island!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:13.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's all right! Don't worry! - OG}It'll be fine! Don't worry about it!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.93,0:17:17.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{They're really pleasant people,\Nand pretty strong, too! - OG}They're all great people,\Nnot to mention super tough!{nao+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.27,0:17:23.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{For eight years, I drew\Nlots of charts and maps... - OG}I've drawn so many charts\Nand maps over the last eight years,{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:25.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{...but this is the only one that's left. - OG}and this is the only one left.{nao+Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.36,0:17:32.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But that's exactly it! This time,\NI'm going to draw charts for me! - OG}But that's just it! This time,\NI'm gonna draw charts for myself!{nao+Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:36.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm going to travel the world\Nwith them - my friends! - OG}I'm gonna travel the world\Nwith them—with my friends!{nao+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:40.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That was my dream, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:42.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:47.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{...I'm not sure when I'll\Ncome back to this island... - OG}So I'm not sure when I'll\Ncome back to this island...{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.39,0:17:58.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm... going now. - OG}Well... I'm off.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:26.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This the last of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:26.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:27.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:28.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Are you finished loading it all? - OG}All done loading?{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.63,0:18:29.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:32.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Now, then. We got lots of\Nprovisions now. - OG}{Now, then. We got\Nloads of provisions now. - Gaijin}Right. We've got plenty\Nof provisions now.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:33.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We're good to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.72,0:18:36.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We were only here a few days,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:39.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{but this island's full of memories, huh? - OG}{but we made tons of\Nmemories on this island, huh? - Gaijin}but we sure made a lot\Nof memories, huh?{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:40.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah! - OG}Yup!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:51.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We owe you a lot\Nfor everything you've done. - OG}We owe you so much for\Neverything you've done.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.07,0:18:54.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We're gonna get back to our\Nprofession of bounty-hunting again! - OG}We're gonna get back\Nto bounty hunting again!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.49,0:18:55.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This is goodbye for now... - OG}We part ways here,{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:58.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,but we look forward to the day\Nwe meet again somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:00.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:03.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– You guys, too!\N– You guys, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:05.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Well, we should get going, too! - OG}Well, it's about time\Nwe shove off, too!{nao+Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:08.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Hold on! What about Nami-san?! - OG}Hey, hold on a sec!\NWhat about Nami?!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.63,0:19:11.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's not coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.05,0:19:13.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Wh...?! Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:17.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You! You made another pass\Nat Nami-san again, didn't you?! - OG}You! You made another\Npass at Nami, didn't you?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:18.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:20.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Oh, yeah. - OG}That reminds me...{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.10,0:19:24.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{She achieved her goal, and she\Nhas no reason to be a pirate, - OG}She did what she set out to do,\Nand she has no reason to be a pirate,{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.23,0:19:27.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{so she might be happier here... - OG}so maybe she'd be happier here...{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:20.10,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{[/an8]No, you definitely did! - OG}{\an8}I {\i1}know{\i0} you did!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.10,0:19:24.23,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{You can't stand that me and Nami-san are all lovey-dovey! - OG}You can't stand that Nami\Nand I are all lovey-dovey!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.23,0:19:25.23,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{[/an8]Are you an idiot? - OG}{\an8}What're you, stupid?{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:26.85,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{[/an8]What'd you call me?! - OG}{\an8}What did you say?!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:29.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What about [/i1]my[/i0] happiness?! - OG}Why can't {\i1}I{\i0} be happier?!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.69,0:19:32.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If Nami-san isn't on the boat, - OG}If Nami isn't on the ship,{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:36.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{then 98.72% of my reason for\Nbeing on the boat is gone! - OG}then 98.72% of my reason\Nfor being here is gone!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:39.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey, you! I couldn't find\Nthe raw ham melon anywhere! - OG}{By the way, I couldn't find the\Nprosciutto and melon anywhere! - Gaijin}Hey, you know, I couldn't find\Nthat ham and melon anywhere!{nao+Goldy}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:40.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Where's Nacchan? - OG}Hey! Where's Nami?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:43.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That's the thing! Nobody's\Nseen her since this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:44.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:46.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,She's leaving all the money behind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:48.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The 100 million berries?! - OG}The full 100 million berries?!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:51.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{She's planning to journey without her money?! - OG}{She's planning to travel\Nwithout her money?! - Gaijin}She's going to travel\Nwithout her money?!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:53.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But she's the one who\Nrisked her life to earn it! - OG}But she risked her life to earn it!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.84,0:19:57.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{She says it's okay because\Nshe'll just steal some more. - OG}She says she'll just steal\Nsome more, so it's all good.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:20:01.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Once that girl says something,\Nthere's no changing her mind. - OG}When she says something,\Nyou can't change her mind.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.39,0:20:02.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:06.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We're the ones who\Nstill haven't thanked her enough! - OG}We're the ones who still have\Nso much to thank her for!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:12.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Nami{-san}!\N– Nami{-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:14.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:14.28,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.28,0:20:16.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Nami-san! - OG}Hey, Nami!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.82,0:20:16.40,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{Nacchan! - OG}It's Nami!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:17.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Get the ship moving!{OG}{Set sail! - Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:26.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Huh? She's started sprinting! - OG}Huh? She started sprinting!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:27.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{She says to get the ship moving. - OG}{She says to set sail. - Gaijin}She said to get moving.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:28.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But...! - OG}{Wait...! - Gaijin}Yeah, but...!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.96,0:20:31.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't tell me she's planning to leave - OG}{Does she really intend to leave - Gaijin}Is she really going to leave{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:35.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,without letting us thank\Nher or say goodbye?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:35.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You can't be serious! - OG}No way!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:37.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Set the sails!{OG}{Hoist the sails! - Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:44.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:45.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{They're setting sail! - OG}They're setting off!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:48.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Wait! We still haven't thanked you! - OG}Wait! We haven't thanked you yet!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.40,0:20:51.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Stop, Nacchan! - OG}Stop, Nami!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.65,0:20:53.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,At least let us thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:54.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{– Nacchan!\N– Nami! Calm down! - OG}– Nami!\N– Nami! Calm down!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:20:58.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hold it! I won't allow\Nyou to leave like this! - OG}Hold it! I won't let you leave like this!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:21:02.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey. Is it okay\Nto let her leave like this? - OG}{Hey, is this how we should\Nlet them say goodbye? - Gaijin}Hey, you sure it's okay\Nto let her leave like this?{nao+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:04.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Why not? It's her decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:23.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:33.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Why?! - OG}What gives?!{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:35.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.42,0:21:56.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,She didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:21:59.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{– Huh?\N– My wallet's gone! - OG}– What's this...?!\N– My wallet's gone!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.09,0:22:01.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.05,0:22:02.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.31,0:22:08.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Take care, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:09.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,How...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:13.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{– How dare you?! You damn brat!\N– How dare you?! You damn brat! - OG}– How dare you?! You rotten brat!\N– How dare you?! You rotten brat!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.94,0:22:17.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey. She hasn't changed a bit. - OG}Hey, she hasn't changed a bit.{Gaijin}{Yup. Same old Nami. - nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:19.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Who knows when she'll\Nbetray us again...? - OG}She might just betray us again...{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.78,0:22:21.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami{-san}! Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.16,0:22:25.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You lousy sneak thief! - OG}{You lousy pickpocket! - Gaijin}You lousy cat burglar!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.78,0:22:26.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.70,0:22:27.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Give back our wallets! - OG}My wallet!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.66,0:22:29.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.08,0:22:30.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Come back anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.83,0:22:31.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Take care of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.96,0:22:33.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We're grateful to you guys! - OG}We appreciate you guys!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.21,0:22:36.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.92,0:22:40.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't forget our promise! - OG}Don't forget your promise!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.47,0:22:47.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Bye, everyone! I'll be back! - OG}{Bye, everyone! I'm heading out! - Gaijin}So long, everyone!\NUntil we meet again!{nao+Goldy}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.85,0:22:52.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{She got us good! - OG}She sure got us!{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:55.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{My own little sister got me! - OG}{My little sister's gonna do great! - Gaijin}My little sister's a piece of work!{Goldy}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:22:58.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Have fun! - OG}{Enjoy yourself! - Gaijin}Have fun out there!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.07,0:23:04.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Here, Genzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.32,0:23:06.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What's this scrap of paper, Doctor? - OG}A piece of paper?\NWhat's this, Doctor?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.20,0:23:11.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That fool. She never learns.\NShe got another tattoo before she left. - OG}{That silly girl. She never learns. She\Ngot another tattoo before she left. - Gaijin}{\q2}That silly girl. She never learns.\NShe wanted a new tattoo before leaving.{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:14.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What mark is this? - OG}{What is this symbol? - Gaijin}What's this symbol?{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.75,0:23:17.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's a tangerine\Nand a pinwheel, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.00,0:23:22.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Huh? Gen-san! What happened to your pinwheel? - OG}Oh? Mr. Gen! What happened\Nto your pinwheel?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:28.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I doubt there's any need for it now. - OG}I won't be needing it anymore.{Viz}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.31,0:23:41.57,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'll be back! - OG}{I'm heading out! - Gaijin}Bell-mère{-san}, I'm off.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.11,0:23:51.41,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hold on, Gen-san! Stay away from Nami! - OG}Hold on, Mr. Gen!\NStay away from Nami!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.87,0:23:55.50,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{No, but, I want to see her smile, too! - OG}Aw, but I wanna see her smile, too!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.50,0:23:58.71,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,She starts crying because\Nyou have such a scary face!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.71,0:24:01.21,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{But what am I supposed\Nto do about that? - OG}Come on, what am I\Nsupposed to do about that?!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.84,0:24:02.38,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.00,0:24:06.30,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{This'll make you laugh, right?! If\NI always keep it here like this?! - OG}If I just keep this right here,\Nit'll make you laugh, won't it?!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.30,0:24:08.34,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{What do you say, Nami-chan? - OG}Well, Nami?!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.34,0:24:11.97,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Look. I really don't think a dumb\Npinwheel is going to make Nami... - OG}Listen, I really don't think a silly ol'\Npinwheel is gonna make Nami...{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.90,0:24:22.02,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Oh. She laughed. - OG}Oh. She's laughing.{Goldy}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.70,0:24:31.37,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,The skies are clear\Nand the winds are fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.37,0:24:35.16,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{And the pinwheel\Nmerrily spins. - OG}And the pinwheel\Nspins merrily for another day.{PP+Polly}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=21}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=18}============================SIGNS AND TITLE=========================
